pdqninja.pdqio
Class FixedSizeSplitter

java.lang.Object
  pdqninja.pdqio.FixedSizeSplitter
All Implemented Interfaces:
Splitter
public class FixedSizeSplitter
extends Object
implements Splitter

Splits a file into fixed sized chunks. The size of the chunk is equal to the blocksize.

Use the FixedSizeSplitter() constructor to evenly divide the file into chunks of blocksize. Use the FixedSizeSplitter(long) constructor to evenly divide the file into chunks of blocksize after skipping initialSkip bytes in the beginning. Use the FixedSizeSplitter(long, long) constructor to evenly divide the file into chunks of blocksize after skipping initialSkip bytes in the beginning, and ensuring that the chunk ends at record boundary, where each record has a length of recordLen.
